<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Shaidar Bangaskiyar Manzanni</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ina ba da gaskiya ga Allah Uba, Mai Iko Duka
 Mahaliccin sama da ƙasa.
 Ina ba da gaskiya ga Yesu Almasihu, Ɗansa Makaɗaici,
 Ubangijinmu,
 Wanda budurwa Maryamu ta ɗauki cikinsa ta wurin ikon
 Ruhu Mai Tsarki,  ta kuma haife shi.
 Ya sha wahala a zamanin Gwamna Buntus Bilatus,
 Aka gicciye shi, ya mutu, aka binne shi,
 Ya shiga lahira.
 A rana ta uku kuwa ya tashi daga matattu.
 Ya koma wurin zamansa a sama yana zaune a hannun dama  na Allah Uba Mai Iko Duka.
 Daga can zai dawo domin yă yi wa masu rai da matattu shari'a.

[V2]
 Ina ba da gaskiya ga Ruhu Mai Tsarki,
 Tsatsarkar Jama'ar Masu Bi ta ko'ina,
 Zumuntar tsarkaka,
 Gafarar zunubai,
 Tashin jiki,
 da rai marar matuƙa. Amin.</lyrics>
</song>